      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fb_china_today",
        "uid": "8633"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t党性和梁家河自觉<br/>\n自动领会中宣部精神<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n共产党和中国人区别对待\t\t</div>",
